{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"08201b90cc","title":"毛泽东关于对学术问题的不同意见不应禁止谈论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d64354f936","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":19,"articleId":"08201b90cc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"419b7ab1ab","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于对学术问题的不同意见不应禁止谈论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"08201b90cc"},{"id":"04cdf17446","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"08201b90cc"},{"id":"2405aa2e65","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、陈、彭真、小平、陈伯达阅，退定一办。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"08201b90cc"},{"id":"3bb5e79fec","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为这种自由谈论，不应当去禁止。这是对学术思想的不同意见，什么人都可以谈论，无所谓损害威信。因此，不要向尤金谈此事。如果国内对此类学术问题和任何领导人有不同意见，也不应加以禁止。如果企图禁止，那是完全错误的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"08201b90cc"},{"id":"971bf2ba93","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"08201b90cc"}],"page":{"id":"024cf932cd","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"08201b90cc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}